			</div>
			<br style="clear: both; height: 0" />
			<div class="content"
				style="background: none repeat scroll 0 0 #FFFFFF; border: 1px solid #E9E9E9; margin: 10px 0 0; padding: 30px;">
				<p>
					<b>${userName}</b> 邀请你加入百知 
				</p>
